that someone left at my house.

154
00:17:28,226 --> 00:17:31,229
- Are you staying?
- Just came by to see how you're doing.

155
00:17:31,437 --> 00:17:33,439
Good. I'm good.

156
00:17:34,232 --> 00:17:35,650
Are you?

157
00:17:37,235 --> 00:17:40,738
Why does everyone
find that so surprising?

158
00:17:40,947 --> 00:17:43,699
