just left for college...

159
00:17:43,950 --> 00:17:46,077
...who you're extremely close with.

160
00:17:46,285 --> 00:17:47,620
I'd be tripping.

161
00:17:47,829 --> 00:17:48,830
Oh, right.

162
00:17:49,080 --> 00:17:52,667
You had a hell of a year too.
The move, the new house...

163
00:17:52,875 --> 00:17:53,876
...the garden.

164
00:17:54,085 --> 00:17:55,169
The car.

165
00:17:55,378 --> 00:17:57,255
