220
00:23:26,209 --> 00:23:28,461
Oh, absolutely. Take your time.

221
00:23:28,669 --> 00:23:30,129
See you soon. Love you.

222
00:23:30,338 --> 00:23:32,215
Love you. Bye.

223
00:23:40,681 --> 00:23:42,308
Cooper!

224
00:23:46,104 --> 00:23:48,106
Cooper!

