234
00:25:13,232 --> 00:25:17,403
Yeah, any procedure where you want
to get the patient immobile, pain-free.

235
00:25:17,612 --> 00:25:18,446
- Hey.
- Hi.

236
00:25:18,654 --> 00:25:20,573
Hi. What are you doing here?

237
00:25:20,782 --> 00:25:21,949
- Are you okay?
- I....

238
00:25:23,284 --> 00:25:24,452
