249
00:25:53,231 --> 00:25:55,566
Did you call about the Feurs?

250
00:25:55,775 --> 00:25:57,652
Oh, yeah.

251
00:25:59,070 --> 00:26:01,781
Harvey says the guy's harmless.
Wouldn't hurt a flea.

252
00:26:01,989 --> 00:26:04,450
Warren. Warren Feur.

253
00:26:04,659 --> 00:26:06,452
What about her?

254
00:26:07,954 --> 00:26:09,747
I know he told me....

255
00:26:10,707 --> 00:26:11,958
Oh.

256
00:26:12,750 --> 00:26:14,836
I met Schumway today.

257
00:26:15,044 --> 00:26:17,255
Who wrote that book you love.

258
00:26:18,214 --> 00:26:21,134
They were doing some spiel
for the chemistry department...

259
00:26:21,342 --> 00:26:23,344
...so Bob Shine introduces us.

260
00:26:24,846 --> 00:26:27,181
You'll love this.
He looks right at me...

261
00:26:27,390 --> 00:26:29,892
...and congratulates me
on Spencer's Theorem.

262
00:26:30,601 --> 00:26:32,645
He didn't know your father was dead?

263
00:26:33,187 --> 00:26:34,188
