264
00:26:35,398 --> 00:26:37,442
Oh, Norman.

265
00:26:38,943 --> 00:26:40,278
What?

266
00:26:40,695 --> 00:26:42,780
You're so sensitive about that.

267
00:26:43,030 --> 00:26:44,282
- No, I'm not.
- You are.

268
00:26:44,490 --> 00:26:46,576
You always overreact.

269
00:26:49,162 --> 00:26:51,372
I'll have to watch that, won't I?

270
00:27:00,757 --> 00:27:02,341
Was it Mary?

271
00:27:02,550 --> 00:27:03,760
Mrs. Feur.

272
00:27:03,968 --> 00:27:06,429
Warren and Mary?

273
00:27:07,930 --> 00:27:09,015
